## Vision

*Why this project exists. The underlying problem and the change in the world it should produce when it works.*

*Write one paragraph that a new contributor (or an agent) can read in 30 seconds and understand what success looks like. Avoid feature lists here — those belong under Goals.*

<Replace this paragraph with one or two sentences describing the project's reason for being. Example: "We are building a self-serve analytics tool for ops teams who today rely on engineers to write SQL. Success looks like a non-technical ops lead answering 80% of their own data questions without filing a ticket.">

