## Goals

*What this project explicitly aims to do. Each goal should be observable — someone outside the project can tell whether it has been achieved.*

- <Goal 1, e.g. "Reduce time-to-answer on common ops questions from days to minutes.">
- <Goal 2, e.g. "Support the top ten recurring report shapes without writing SQL.">
- <Goal 3, e.g. "Stay within the existing analytics warehouse — no new data infrastructure.">

Add or remove bullets to fit the project. Keep this list short — typically 3 to 6 goals. A long Goals list usually means the project's scope is still negotiable.

