## Constraints

*Technical, organizational, or time-shaped constraints that meaningfully shape decisions. List things that would make a reviewer say "wait, why did we go that way?" if not documented.*

- <Constraint 1, e.g. "Python 3.11 only — the warehouse client doesn't support newer versions yet.">
- <Constraint 2, e.g. "No external paid services in the critical path; the team's procurement cycle is six weeks.">
- <Constraint 3, e.g. "Must run on the existing Kubernetes cluster; no new VPC or cloud account.">

